name: WorkoutRoulette
0:
”Alexa, spin workout roulette”
”Give me a workout”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spin workout roulette
des: Want to change up your daily workout? Ask Alexa to spin workout roulette! You'll be told to do between 1-15 reps of jumping jacks, push ups, curl-ups, squats, high kicks, burpees, tuck jumps, or high knees.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
